# Assignment 4: DHCP Configuration

## Objective
To configure a DHCP server on a router and assign IP addresses automatically to clients.

---

## Configuration

enable  
configure terminal  

ip dhcp pool xyz  
network 192.168.10.0 255.255.255.0  
dns-server 1.2.3.4  
lease 0 3  
exit  

no service dhcp bootp  

---

## Client Configuration

Set PC to obtain IP address automatically (DHCP).

